...I'd have
been worth a fortune.

25:21.790 --> 25:23.165
What the..

25:24.290 --> 25:25.750
Ah.

25:30.458 --> 25:33.081
...about, you know,
you've got to have this

25:33.083 --> 25:34.206
and you've got
to have that

